Gray Area Festival is San Francisco's premier annual festival advancing culture and common good through the lens of art and technology.

Fri Forjindam
http://www.mycotoo.com

Fri Forjindam is Chief Development Officer for Mycotoo, Inc., a global leader in themed entertainment, live events and immersive brand experiences. AsaCameroonian-born, NewOrleans-schooled,MFA graduate of Columbia University in NYC, Fri has workedin film, theatre, publishing, live events and experience design. Shebrings her rich background in content development and experiential marketing to facilitatedevelopment strategies forregional, national and international tourism.
Fri brings a unique perspective to the strategic discussions about industry trends, challenges and the future of themed entertainment and experience design.
